# Enforce LF line endings for all text files across platforms so the working
# tree, git index, and Biome (formatter.lineEnding defaults to lf) all agree.
# This overrides a local core.autocrlf=true that otherwise checks out CRLF and
# makes Biome flag every line. Run `git add --renormalize .` after adding this.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary assets — never normalize.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.webp binary
*.avif binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.otf binary
*.pdf binary
